::Prowl::

Prowl frowns, looking out over the battlefield and seeing that
Cliffjumper was right. IR's thoughts had stopped coming to him, and he
knew that she had blocked him out. He nods and looks at Iron Raptor.

"I think the Element has working CR chambers. We might wanna get the
wounded into them before they all die. Do I have authorization to do
that, commander?" Prowl says to Iron Raptor, wanting to do this right
and listen to her authority for once.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., robertdahl <rdahl@t...> wrote:
> Cliffjumper ran towards Iron Raptor and Prowl, then bent over and
panted
> heavily, his injurys taking their toll on him. "We're getting
> slaughtered out here, any orders?" he asked, as his wounds began to

you
> guys look like you need a recharge" he suggested.
